    "The rationale behind the bilingual requirements is the historical context of operations at Austrian Post (in German) and the internationalization of the organization in terms of the team structure (in English).",
    "In addition, some projects are outsourced to external contractors, wherein the interactions are often in English.",
    "However, most TSs are specified in English, with the project's key vocabulary (e.g., system names and project keywords) maintained primarily in German.",
